data.description: Discover serenity in Creekview Village w/ this 3BR home boasting a large bonus room & nature views. Conveniently located near I-24 for easy commutes, this home offers privacy w/ no backyard neighbors on a nearly half acre wooded lot. The deck overlooks Spring Creek, providing a scenic retreat - complete with fire pit. Recent upgrades include brand new hardwood flooring & stainless steel appliances. The owner's suite features a double vanity, along w/ a separate shower & tub. With creek access for outdoor adventures and a charming covered front porch, this 2100+ sqft home combines modern elegance with natural beauty. Neighborhood also includes community park & playground. Don't miss out on this perfect blend of convenience and tranquility! Seller offering $10K toward Buyer Closing Expenses!
